name: Battle Royale—In Hindsight
description:
The victor. After it's all over, does anything matter anymore?

—

Animated loop. A study of negative space and form. I was suffering a creative block, and thought I would try a different approach, stay loose. I smattered the canvas with a sizable blob of void. I let my eraser do the talking.  I started to carve a form out; It organically manifested into a snapshot of a moment—of things I've been feeling, but can't say.
